item.title: [PI] Jad Help [PI]
item.dc:creator: @Sagi Sagi
item.description:
@Sagi wrote:

I think i know how to solve this one. This must be the MTP V2 by marcbob

Go to ActionHandler.java and search for ‘case 9356’. You’ll get something like this:

		case 9356:
			//c.getPA().enterCaves();
			c.sendMessage("Temporarily removed due to bugs.");
		break;

Okay, just change it to this.

		case 9356:
			c.getPA().enterCaves();
			c.sendMessage("You are going to fight Jad. Good luck.");
		break;

It was disabled, may be due to some bugs. Hope you can fix the bugs. Good Luck.
Hope I help.
